evaluation_questions.question: Does participation in this entity produce an educative dividend?
Does this entity allow participation in goals as well as tasks?
If yes (#2), is participation in goals direct/representative? Choose YES for direct and No for represenative.
Does this entity allow participants to maintain control or ownership of resources produced?
If yes (#3),  collective or individual control? YES for collective, NO for individual
Is there the capacity for exit (with resources or without penalty)?
Is there the capacity for effective voice (feedback, dissent or protest)?
Are there metrics of participation? Can a participant see, measure or experience the outcome of their participation?
Does the entity itself provide the capacity for communication (affective, subjective, rational or other meaningful intercourse) between participants in some form?
